content:
Share Edit Access for Record Collections with Other Users

You can now update collections with others by sharing write permissions for record collections with different users or groups. This applies to Einstein Conversation Insights in Lightning Experience.

To share a collection, select the collection record and click Share Collection. The Read/Write option is now available to share with groups or individual users.

Users with Read/Write permission can add or remove records from collections and also share access with others.
title: Share Edit Access for Record Collections in Salesforce
